<ListItem><Paragraph Foreground="{DynamicResource ColorBrush1}"><Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E4%B8%8B%E7%95%8C%E7%9F%B3%E8%8B%B1%E7%9F%BF%E7%9F%B3" Margin="0,0,0,-8">下界石英矿石</local:MyTextButton></Underline>也可以被烧炼为<Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E4%B8%8B%E7%95%8C%E7%9F%B3%E8%8B%B1" Margin="0,0,0,-8">下界石英</local:MyTextButton></Underline>，每烧炼一个会给予0.2 经验值。</Paragraph></ListItem>
